snippet.title: The AmberTURD Incident
snippet.description:
This is basically me ranting about Amber Heard's "dirty thirty" and how she yet again abused not only Johnny Depp but all those around him. 
If you're here for true crime, I plan on uploading some true crime here this week 
Thank you everyone who follows me, this week has been a whirlwind and I'm just so grateful. 
Also a BIG thank you for your patience! It’s up! So much more already in the making for both Justice for Johnny and for true crime!
My brother Marcus edited this video! Go subscribe to him for our family antics! :) - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCH24XjKjw7YXjgWdZ-HTGAw
To get more educated on this case you can visit:
Nick Wallis’ Website for the Court Docs - https://www.nickwallis.com/depp-trial

Incredibly Average (That Brian Fella) for audio recordings and his very investigated stance – https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg0C-N_MPYYOXyF4T3jMxNQ/featured
Full unedited 2 hour audio here – https://youtu.be/lslHx-nHjzc
For current case updates check out That Umbrella Guy here - https://www.youtube.com/user/GranularHeaven
And if you haven’t yet, come see me on Tiktok! https://www.tiktok.com/@delloliod?lang=en
Or, come follow me on Twitter https://twitter.com/delloliod
